title: VPFL
author: VD
content_html: Okay, who is in this year? Those who haven’t participated before will take precedence over past players. Remember, it’s a keeper league, so you’ll inherit up to three players from last season if you want to keep them. The draft will be Sun Aug 30 3:30pm Central.
